name: DockOn
overview: DockOn, Inc. is a new wireless technology company based in San Diego, CA. DockOn has pioneered CPL™ design tools, allowing DockOn to offer the first commercially viable two-dimensional planar compound antenna. Proprietary CPL™ designs are revolutionary in antenna technology. The CPL™ technology allows DockOn to create customized antennas for our partners and customers that are smaller, more efficient and result in a lower BOM count than any other antenna available on the market today. Our business model is to develop custom, licensable antenna designs for WiFi and a wide variety of M2M wireless devices and applications.
